function Y = AddPolyPhase_bp(x,Y,phase)%ADDPOLYPHASE adds a polynomial phase.%	ADDPOLYPHASE(X,Y,PHASE) Adds the phase, PHASE, to Y given X.%%	Calculates the function:%	Y = Y .* exp(i *polyval(fliplr(phase),x));%	$Revision: 1.2 $ $Date: 2001/10/22 23:20:24 $%%	$Log: AddPolyPhase.m,v $%	Revision 1.2  2001/10/22 23:20:24  zeekec%	Fixed help%	%	Revision 1.1  2001/10/22 19:01:54  zeekec%	New function%	Y = Y .* exp(i *polyval(fliplr(phase),x));